Architecture becomes queryable, enforceable, and measurable.

If design intent changes, downstream evidence invalidates automatically. Architecture is no longer documentation. It is a living guardrail embedded in delivery.

In Jurassic Park terms — the fences don't just hold. They report. They adapt. And they never forget which dinosaur they were built to contain."


